text: Mochammad Supriadi (born 23 May 2002) is an Indonesian professional footballer who plays as a winger for Liga 1 club Persebaya Surabaya and the Indonesia under-19 team.https://www.bolalob.com/amp/read/92585/biodata-pemain-timnas- indonesia-u-16-Muhammad-Faskal-Wilmar ==Career== ===Persebaya Surabaya=== Supriadi made his first-team debut on 24 August 2019 as a substitute in a match against Persija Jakarta.
